the present issue 1 the respondent issued a notice of assessment to the applicant on 15 november 2005 for its income tax liability under the income tax assessment act 1936 (cth) (the 1936 act) and the income tax assessment act 1997 (cth) (the 1997 act) for the year ended 30 june 2002 of $31,490 which was due for payment on 15 may 2003 (the assessment).
a notice of assessment of penalty of $23,618 for having a tax shortfall amount in respect of that financial year (the penalty assessment) was issued to the applicant on 25 november 2005.
